Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.90,0:21:07.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是不是幫到哥哥了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.43,0:21:09.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,妹妹們
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.00,0:21:11.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大姐姐我也努力了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.54,0:21:20.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊啊 我肚子餓了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.08,0:21:21.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,說起來我也是
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.83,0:21:24.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,從昨天開始就什麼都沒吃了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.02,0:21:26.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好想念蛋黃醬啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.72,0:21:28.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,累的時候就該吃豆沙包
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.71,0:21:30.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,偶爾吃吃果凍也不錯啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.09,0:21:32.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那麼回去後
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.20,0:21:34.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們就先吃早餐吧喵
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.89,0:21:36.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我會大展身手
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.20,0:21:38.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不惜餘力的做的喵
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.20,0:21:43.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那麼果然是要吃咖喱啊 班長
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.30,0:21:45.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,肉好 我要吃肉
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.92,0:21:50.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,主君 主君
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.95,0:21:53.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯？什麼？曉
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.18,0:21:57.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,總之 辛苦你了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.51,0:22:03.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也辛苦你了 曉
