Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.78,0:23:51.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們開動了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:54.47,0:23:55.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,說起來 大叔呢
Dialogue: 0,0:23:55.93,0:23:57.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,還在修理通信設備呢
Dialogue: 0,0:23:58.67,0:24:01.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以 我們就是李耿恩的護衛嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:24:01.24,0:24:02.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好想泡澡啊
Dialogue: 0,0:24:02.85,0:24:04.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是也挺好的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:24:04.81,0:24:08.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,機會難得 要不要來較量一下？
Dialogue: 0,0:24:08.67,0:24:10.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 大叔不見了
Dialogue: 0,0:24:10.88,0:24:12.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,逃跑了
Dialogue: 0,0:24:13.09,0:24:15.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,麻婆還有好多呢
Dialogue: 0,0:24:15.40,0:24:18.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不 主君該吃下一碗咖喱了
